<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<html xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd">
    <body>
        <h2>How to Export a Termbase</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Select <span class="Emphasis">Resources &gt; Export Termbase</span>.</li>
            <li>From the <span class="Emphasis">Termbase to export</span> drop-down, select the termbase you want to export. </li>
            <li>Next to the <span class="Emphasis">TBX File</span> field, click <img src="../../../Images/Shared/All/Interface/Buttons/Browse-Ellipses-btn.png" class="ReduceButtonSize" />. </li>
            <li>Locate an existing TBX file you want to overwrite, or enter a name for a new TBX file.</li>
            <li>Click <b>Save</b>. </li>
            <li>Click <span class="Emphasis">Start Export</span>.</li>
        </ol>
    </body>
</html>